{"tid":855754,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"有乜方法可以阻止起天價人工島？","createTime":"2018-10-10T08:47:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-11T03:22:07.000Z","uid":164090,"like":43,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"bbc70e4a9eeb57534b4eebfd11a861fb2593b37f","tid":855754,"uid":164090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T08:47:56.000Z","msg":"人工島根本痴撚線！<br />\n<br />\n解決土地問題根本有好多方法<br />\n1) 新界，高球場etc 大撚把地<br />\n2)  停止輸入每日150大陸人<br />\n<br />\n人工島本身又存在大量問題！<br />\n1) 環境嚴重破壞<br />\n2) 全球水位上漲，小島存在極大風險<br />\n3) 天文數目既造價，仲未計通脹！<br />\n<br />\n依個計劃目的根本為撚左：<br />\n1) 官商勾結<br />\n2) 比錢共產黨<br />\n3) 等再多啲大陸人落嚟沖淡香港文化<br />\n<br />\n我真係唔想睇住香港變成咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n集思廣益，大家一齊計劃下點先可以阻止到依個垃圾政府起天價人工島..."},{"pid":"3721758abec4bcb067b168b2903de0a3f197424f","tid":855754,"uid":120123,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T08:49:23.000Z","msg":"政變<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86cdddae5be1a1758a1a693b8a82e770e021300f","tid":855754,"uid":65887,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T08:49:30.000Z","msg":"全球水位上漲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d020a1f29a5691a967a6d8a63efcffaae9fde2e4","tid":855754,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T08:51:43.000Z","msg":"起天價其他野都會"},{"pid":"f3420e91fe8f14eee8251c46e1be4e98f9e53d9f","tid":855754,"uid":28181,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"3721758abec4bcb067b168b2903de0a3f197424f","tid":855754,"uid":120123,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T08:49:23.000Z","msg":"政變<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T08:52:54.000Z","msg":"社會撕裂 大家都輸 是時候政變了"},{"pid":"4115b40d462a758f646b3f90a7b990158f5609a0","tid":855754,"uid":61589,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"86cdddae5be1a1758a1a693b8a82e77