) 全球水位上漲，小島存在極大風險<br />\n3) 天文數目既造價，仲未計通脹！<br />\n<br />\n依個計劃目的根本為撚左：<br />\n1) 官商勾結<br />\n2) 比錢共產黨<br />\n3) 等再多啲大陸人落嚟沖淡香港文化<br />\n<br />\n我真係唔想睇住香港變成咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n集思廣益，大家一齊計劃下點先可以阻止到依個垃圾政府起天價人工島...</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n計劃目的那三樣，應該係陰謀論。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">正確係林鄭怕得罪大陸和得罪左膠大愛人士（所以唔敢cut 150），又唔敢得罪有錢佬（高球場），又伯得罪行山人士（郊野公園條例）。<br />\n<br />\n又知本港高地價問題嚴峻<br />\n求其諗個solution當自己做左野<br />\n<br />\n唔認真諗下其他alternative solution</span><br />\n<br />\n</blockquote>"},{"pid":"019c1450081cbf34a589ab3efbe00b7cb13cfe24","tid":855754,"uid":44152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T09:03:59.000Z","msg":"再咁搞法應該會有比雨傘運動更嚴重嘅示威運動"},{"pid":"7a9d8f52639fd9947b69d399b1d2fa3d824836a4","tid":855754,"uid":197852,"like":2,"dislike":12,"score":-10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T09:04:08.000Z","msg":"阻你老母<br />\n我讀civil"},{"pid":"9e0a12cc2b76271ad32f3b06f367afc30ff1aaaf","tid":855754,"uid":145496,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T09:05:13.000Z","msg":"應該黎個全港版魚蛋"},{"pid":"84d4285587d51f05c05e0a85e111aa5ecd7a95f9","tid":855754,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T10:26:31.000Z","msg":"荊軻"},{"pid":"688d1aa2df9cccadc82d9b7890eb495cd487041e","tid":855754,"uid":164090,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9e0a12cc2b76271ad32f3b06f367afc30ff1aaaf","tid":855754,"uid":145496,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T09:05:13.000Z","msg":"應該黎個全港版魚蛋"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T14:10:13.000Z","msg":"我都想，香港人如果做到咁團結好多問題都解決到"},{"pid":"aa23839c60f28753734ae1758b663079b70647c9","tid":855754,"uid":127952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7a9d8f52639fd9947b69d399b1d2fa3d824836a4","tid":855754,"uid":197852,"like":2,"dislike":12,"score":-10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T09:04:08.000Z","msg":"阻你老母<br />\n我讀civil"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T14:19:07.00